{"type":"message","id":"21c9ab68","parentId":"7ae30e06","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:44:44.242Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-12 10:43 GMT+9] 了解、続けよう。\nまずは PATH の永続修正 → device-auth.json/権限まわりの EPERM 切り分け → LINE webhook 受信確認 の順で進めるのがきれいだよ。必要なら各ステップのコマンドをそのまま一緒に整理する。"}],"timestamp":1773279884238}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa04f44c","parentId":"21c9ab68","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:44:47.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] はーい、続きやろっか。既定モデルは `ollama/qwen3.5:9b` だけど、今は別のランタイムで見てるよ。まずは PATH の永続修正から順に詰めようか、それとも 3 ステップ分のコマンドをまとめて一気に整理しようか？","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0d9c6bc196a10e200169b21a9170408191ba2da06528d3ec45\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":535,"output":92,"cacheRead":16256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16883,"cost":{"input":0.0013375000000000001,"output":0.00138,"cacheRead":0.004064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0067815}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773279884240}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"0c2ad3d9","parentId":"fa04f44c","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:44:55.333Z","summary":"## Goal\n- (none)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Output only the structured summary in the exact requested format.\n- Preserve existing summary information and add only any newly discovered context.\n- Keep the summary concise.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] No conversation content was provided.\n- [x] Preserved the existing empty-state summary because no new conversation messages were available to incorporate.\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Waiting for actual conversation details to summarize.\n\n### Blocked\n- No source conversation content to summarize.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Return an empty-state summary**: The provided conversation was empty, so only a minimal structured checkpoint can be produced.\n- **Preserve prior summary unchanged in substance**: No new conversation content was present to modify the existing checkpoint.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Provide the conversation content to summarize.\n2. Regenerate the structured checkpoint summary from that content.\n\n## Critical Context\n- The supplied conversation block was empty:\n  ```\n  <conversation>\n\n  </conversation>\n  ```\n- No new conversation messages were provided beyond the prior empty-state context.","firstKeptEntryId":"21c9ab68","tokensBefore":16883,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":false}
