{"type":"message","id":"b1ce3dd6","parentId":"ce3ec0fc","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:47:00.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 了解。じゃあその順で、実行しやすい形でまとめるね。\n\n### 1) PATH の永続修正\nPowerShell で:\n\n```powershell\n$openclawDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\"\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\n  \"Path\",\n  (([Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\",\"User\").TrimEnd(';') + \";$openclawDir\") -replace ';;+',';'),\n  \"User\"\n)\n$env:Path = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\",\"User\") + \";\" + [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\",\"Machine\")\nwhere.exe openclaw\nopenclaw --version\n```\n\nもし `where.exe openclaw` で出なければ、まず実体確認:\n\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw*\"\n```\n\n### 2) `device-auth.json` / 権限まわりの EPERM 切り分け\nまず場所確認:\n\n```powershell\n$auth = Join-Path $env:USERPROFILE \".openclaw\\credentials\\device-auth.json\"\n$dir  = Split-Path $auth\nWrite-Host \"auth=$auth\"\nTest-Path $auth\nGet-Item $dir | Format-List FullName,Attributes\n```\n\n権限・属性チェック:\n\n```powershell\nattrib $auth\nicacls $auth\nicacls $dir\n```\n\nOpenClaw を完全停止してから再試行:\n\n```powershell\nGet-Process | Where-Object {$_.ProcessName -match 'openclaw|node'} | Select-Object Id,ProcessName,Path\n```\n\n怪しいプロセスがいたら止める:\n\n```powershell\nStop-Process -Id <PID> -Force\n```\n\nそのうえで、読み取り専用や壊れた ACL を疑うなら:\n\n```powershell\nattrib -R $auth\nicacls $auth /inheritance:e\nicacls $auth /grant \"$env:USERNAME:(F)\"\n```\n\nもしファイル破損やロックが濃そうなら、バックアップして再生成:\n\n```powershell\nCopy-Item $auth \"$auth.bak-$(Get-Date -Format yyyyMMdd-HHmmss)\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nRemove-Item $auth -Force\n```\n\nそのあと再ログイン:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw login\n```\n\n### 3) LINE webhook 受信確認\nまず OpenClaw 側の状態確認:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw status\nopenclaw channels status --probe\n```\n\nGateway が死んでたら:\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway status\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nログを見ながら webhook を叩いたときの反応確認。Windows なら OpenClaw を前面で起動して見るのが早いこともあるけど、まずは状態確認優先でOK。\n\nLINE Developers 側では:\n- Webhook URL が正しい\n- `Use webhook` が ON\n- `Verify` で 200 が返る\n- Bot の応答権限/チャネル設定が有効\n\n### すすめ方\nまずはこの順で結果だけ返してくれれば、次をその場で絞れるよ:\n\n1. `where.exe openclaw`\n2. `openclaw --version`\n3. `attrib $auth`\n4. `icacls $auth`\n5. `openclaw status`\n6. `openclaw channels status --probe`\n\n必要なら次で、**コピペ一発の診断スクリプト**にまとめる。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0d9c6bc196a10e200169b21b0848e48191b1544947ec3a5035\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":633,"output":822,"cacheRead":16256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17711,"cost":{"input":0.0015825000000000001,"output":0.01233,"cacheRead":0.004064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0179765}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773280002907}}
